    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Tachydromia fuscinervis (Frey), male (USA, Alaska; CNC). A. Habitus, lateral view. B. Hypopygium, dorsal view. C. Right epandrial lamella, right surstylus and right cercus, lateral view. D. Left epandrial lamella and left surstylus, lateral view. Abbreviations: cerc—cercus; lft sur—left surstylus; rt cerc—right cercus; rt sur—right surstylus. B–D: scale bar is 0.1 mm." ;
